FastPattern.description: 1, ServiceWarning: failed to lookup current person in Subject
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {\w+-\d+-\d+} [^:]+: failed to lookup current person in Subject:
\[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {\w+-\d+-\d+} [^:]+: INVALID_CREDENTIALS: Failed to Jaas EAS authenticate
\[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {\w+-\d+-\d+} [^:]+: Verify Password failed\. Unable to authenticate

FastPattern.matcher: \[(.*?),(\d+)\] \[(\w+)\]\(\S+\) {.*} [^:]+: "Request URI (\S+) targeted by ([-\w.]+) not found in allowed delegator list\.\s*(.*)
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: "Request URI \S+ targeted by [-\w.]+ not found in allowed delegator list

FastField.defaultValue: Request URI "$4" not found in allowed delegator list

FastPattern.description: 12, ServiceWarning: {Displaying error page, sending error page back, Programming error}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:Displaying error page to user|Error: sending error page back to browser|Programming error)

FastPattern.description: 13, ServiceWarning: {failed to lookup person object, Lookup failed}
19, ServiceWarning: {error encountered, Username or Password is null, encountered problem}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+:\s*\S*:?\s*(?:An error was encountered trying to get the user account information|Username or Password is null/empty-string|encountered problem)

FastPattern.description: 20, ServiceWarning: {Jaas EAS password cannot be null, failed to find user}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:Jaas EAS password cannot be null|Failed to find user in Jaas EAS)

FastPattern.description: 22, ServiceWarning: {Failed to decrypt secret, Failed to communicated, failed to set session data, Failed to remove session}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: [F|f]ailed to(?: decrypt secret| communicated with| set session data| remove session)

FastPattern.description: 24, ServiceWarning: {getResponse failed, Unable to track HTTP session}
25, ServiceWarning: Secret entry couldn't be decrypted
26, ServiceWarning: {problem refreshing the mail server, Error getting attribute}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:There was a problem refreshing the mail server cache|Error getting \w+ attribute)

FastPattern.description: 28, ServiceWarning: possible problematic rdb connection detected
30, ServiceWarning: Caught an illegal argument exception
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: Caught an illegal argument exception while trying to format an object

FastPattern.description: 31, ServiceWarning: An attempt was made to access the login
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: An Attempt was made to access the [\w ]+ via \w+

FastPattern.description: 32, ServiceWarning: unable to update recovery password for user
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: unable to update recovery password for user: \d+

FastPattern.description: 34, ServiceWarning: {Unknown error code; unexpected setup error;unable to delete node;Cannot re-register}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:Unknown error code|unexpected setup error|Unable to delete node \w+|Cannot re-register)

FastPattern.description: 35, ServiceWarning: {Session is not registered; taID expired and deleted}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:Session \S+ does is not registered|taID=\d+ expired and deleted)

FastPattern.description: 36, ServiceWarning: {Hibernate Dialect must be explicitly set;Unable to start rendering channel; Channel ID character cache has invalid size)
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:Hibernate Dialect must be explicitly set|Unable to start rendering channel|Channel ID character cache has invalid size)

FastPattern.description: 37, ServiceWarning: {The EAS context ldap is disabled;notify expiredsession; channelrendererfactory}
39, ServiceWarning: {failed to contruct channel; session already invalidated}
40, ServiceWarning: {lastactive request cancelled; deauthenticate request cancelled}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:lastactive request cancelled for \S+|deauthenticate request cancelled for \S+)

FastPattern.description: 42, ServiceWarning: {An error occured updating your account; authentication failed; lastactive request failed;Resetting error}
FastPattern.pattern: \[.*?,\d+\] \[\w+\]\(\S+\) {.*?} [^:]+: (?:An error occurred updating your account|\w+ authentication failed but should never fail|lastactive request failed|Resetting error)
